Nicole Scherzinger begins her fun Instagram saga at a roadside services after the Free Live Radio concert

The opening scene, shot on a smartphone on Saturday and posted on Sunday, is her mouth-wide-open shock and delight at seeing a Papa John's at the services.

'Here's alit story, an adventure with #Scherzy when she's on the #Run after a show and discovers a service station in the #UK!' she posted with a sneaky plug for her single Run from her second solo album Big Fat Lie.

But then came her disappointment at said pizza joint being closed.

After her excitement at seeing a Papa John's, the singer is disappointed to see the pizza outlet closed

