'Sweet baby Jesus! there's a #PapaJohns in the UK! Wait, What?! It's not open???'

All wasn't lost though for our intrepid adventurer though, with a taste of her home in the US, Kentucky, on offer.

'But wait! #KFC is still open, taking me back, to back home #KY. Live it, love it taste it, Who doesn't want some of that!?'

Of course, it was then time for a romantic interlude in the former X Factor judge's little tale with the love interest being a Krispy Kreme outlet - she was so taken by the sugary treats her hashtag was all-encompassing.

'Is that a #krispykreme I dare see?! #everything,' she posted

