Chocolate bars served as the stars for the big finale, though we doubt their ending is as happy as Scherzinger's.  

'My adventure has come to an end and I figured why not top it off with some English candy bars! I love this country and their service stations.'

Unfortunately, it is not known which services exactly received such praise from the star, but surely it won't be long until they're cashing in on the Scherzinger seal of approval.

 

